Wassup wsssup yall… thank yall for all the prayers and kind words….i believe in the power of prayer and love you all more than you know.  As a lot of you know, I had a massive heart attack out of nowhere about a year and a half ago and was life flighted to Vanderbilt and they saved my life.  I was even shocked with the grays anatomy paddles and the whole 9 lol.  Well the other night I was having shortness of breath and was debating on whether or not I should come to hospital or not but it was getting so hard to breathe that I had to.  I got here and was given a bunch of shiity news.  I’ve been low on blood like actual blood and had a blood transfusion which has helped a lot with my breathing issues as Oxygen is in our blood.  The doctors ran some tests and don’t know where the blood is going.  I had fluid on my lungs and they actually drained 3 liters of fluid in 3 hrs yesterday.  The Dr told me if I had waited 2 more weeks I probably would have died and not know why.  They ran tests on my heart and came back that only 20% of my heart is working.  They are doing a colonoscopy and indiscopy sometime@this week to try and find where all the blood is going that I was missing. They also have to go back in my chest and see what’s going on in there.  Needless to say I’ve been upset and worried to death (no pun intended) lol. I have a lot of great cool friends that have been checking on me constantly and am@still hoping for the best!  I love God and believe in him and the miracles he can make happen so there’s still hope and light at the end of my tunnel.  I’m a tough mofo and with yallls prayers I think I’m gonna pull through!  i had no clue how close to death I actually was so if u or  a loved one are debating on getting something checked out that concerns you  just do it!  If you’re mad or angry at someone, forgive them as it is the biggest part of the Bible and nobody should walk around harboring any ill feelings towards anyone.  Life is precious but life is short in this realm.  Be kind to one another, love and forgive each other and y’all will feel so much better.  I’ll keep everyone posted but yall can hit up @st8linejabbs for updates. 🙏🙏❤️
